What’s your “why”?
I started training with weights in high school, because that’s what my basketball team did and I blindly followed because I wanted to be a part of the team! 😂 Would have never thought my life would get so involved with something that makes my body hurt so much 😅 but the perspective, the intention, the goals change as you progress. 
Thank you for everyone that has joined in on the journey, friends/family/followers/haters, all have a special place in my heart!
